                "invention-title": [
                    "Technical method for preparing lithium phosphate from lithium-containing glass powder",
                    "一种含锂玻璃粉制备磷酸锂的技术方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a technical method for preparing lithium phosphate from lithium-containing glass powder. The preparation method comprises the following steps: firstly, stirring and mixing powder forms of the lithium-containing glass powder (Li2O.Al2O3.SiO2.B2O3.MgO) and the ferrophosphorus slag (FePO4/C) in proportion by a dry method to obtain a precursor, and calcining the precursor in an inert environment at the temperature of 600-800 DEG C for 3-8 hours to obtain a calcined mixed product; dissolving the calcined product with sulfuric acid, controlling the pH value to be 1-1.5, adding 5-10% hydrogen peroxide into the calcined product, controlling the temperature to be 80-100 DEG C, stirring and reacting for 10-30 minutes, filtering and separating to obtain a filtrate which is a lithium sulfate solution and a filter cake which is a phosphorus-containing insoluble substance; and adding sodium hydroxide into the filtrate to adjust the pH value to 4-5, filtering to remove insoluble substances to obtain an impurity-removed lithium sulfate solution, adding a filter cake into a 5-8% sodium hydroxide solution, and resolving phosphorus to obtain a sodium phosphate solution. And heating the sodium phosphate solution into the lithium sulfate solution, boiling and filtering to obtain lithium phosphate, and the comprehensive recovery rate of lithium reaches 85%."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种含锂玻璃粉制备磷酸锂的技术方法。其制备过程是：按比例先将含锂玻璃粉（Li2O·Al2O3·SiO2·B2O3·MgO）和磷铁渣（FePO4/C）的粉末形态干法搅拌混合得到前驱体，置于惰性环境下600~800℃煅烧3~8h，得到煅烧混合产物。将煅烧产物通过硫酸溶解，pH控制1~1.5，煅烧产物加入5~10%双氧水，控制温度在80~100℃下搅拌反应10~30min，过滤分离，滤液为硫酸锂溶液，滤饼为含磷不溶物。滤液加氢氧化钠调节pH至4~5，过滤除去不溶物得到除杂硫酸锂溶液，滤饼加入到5~8%氢氧化钠溶液中，解析出磷得到磷酸钠溶液。磷酸钠溶液加热到硫酸锂溶液中，煮沸过滤得到磷酸锂，锂综合回收率达到85%。"
                }
            ]
